::Battera::

"That's ok.  Don't worry about it.  I guess I might seam strange to someone 
who has never seen one like me before."
She looked down the hallway for a moment.  She thought of the lab where she 
left her friends.  She jerked her head to the side. She closed her eyes and 
cleared her mind of the thought.  She turned her head back and looked at 
Cybershark.  She felt that conflict again.
"I have to go now." she said in a soft voice.  "Thank you again for your 
help.  But I should be going."  She looked at the floor and started to walk 
down the hallway to the entrance of the base.
